window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I'm not Goth to hide my Drow heritage, I'm Goth because I'm not a quitter.</p> <p>My name is Cheyenne Summerlin, remember that name. Somebody should...</p> <p>The world can't know I'm a Drow halfling. Not yet. I barely have these powers under my control, but time's up. I'm about to take magic for a test drive. Want to come along?</p> <p>The black ops government group believe they can run my life... But I have plans of my own.</p> <p>Watch out magical evil doers - I'm about to crash your party.</p> <p>But will my training be enough?</p>"; 
